NNQT_istance: What is the last bodyofwaters in Germany for areaofcatchments?
correct_NNQT_istance: What is the last bodyofwaters in Germany for areaofcatchments?
query: SELECT ?uri WHERE  { ?uri rdf:type <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/BodyOfWater>; <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/areaOfCatchment> ?measure; <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/location> <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany>  }ORDER BY ASC(?elevation) LIMIT 1

NNQT_istance: What is the last mountainranges in Germany for lengths?
correct_NNQT_istance: What is the last mountain ranges in Germany for lengths?
query: SELECT ?uri WHERE  { ?uri rdf:type <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/MountainRange>; <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/length> ?measure; <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/country> <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany>  }ORDER BY ASC(?elevation) LIMIT 1
